{"tid":257653,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果可以翻返以前重新開始，但所有野都唔會改變，你肯唔肯？","createTime":"2017-05-25T12:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T07:09:52.000Z","uid":40757,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb6c7744fe4e9a37e8b10b37f8626add90e3919","tid":257653,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"如果可以翻返去以前<br />\n翻到去幾前你自己可以決定（例如出世、10歲，兩年前etc)<br />\n你會帶埋記憶返去，但係唔會改變到任何一個動作<br />\n你可以用呢個第一身感受多次過去發生既所有野<br />\n但就好似一條寄生蟲/旁觀者咁<br />\n你唔可以控制過去既自己，亦都冇辦法同過去既自己交流<br />\n所以所有野都唔會改變<br />\n只係重新發生一次<br />\n<br />\n肯：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔肯：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好可以講下點解"},{"pid":"ead58bf17542cfec701a7a62c4cf2ba1b8bc0c33","tid":257653,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"aa47ccc2710a9f5bebb96020f939d01988c7a698","tid":257653,"uid":15323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"返去托啊咁"},{"pid":"ee94bc76c24b1463c0fdf72b1d5d5382153671ed","tid":257653,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返去托啊咁</blockquote><br />\n同問"},{"pid":"866c7bb5f37cea292f0cf94cbecf20ad76d0dc4e","tid":257653,"uid":101693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返去托啊咁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600a50c14920bccfd3c0f0392abe558dc29f5d3e","tid":257653,"uid":81734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8818594d904192f9858dc9cb28b2c0006e510836","tid":257653,"uid":87108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:45:24.000Z","msg":"咁我睇facebook啲回顧好過啦"},{"pid":"2d631a29